library(ggplot2)
library(forecast)
## Registered S3 method overwritten by 'quantmod':
##   method            from
##   as.zoo.data.frame zoo
ts <- ts(AirPassengers, frequency = 12)
autoplot(ts) + xlab("Year") + ylab("Passenger Count") + ggtitle("Time Series Plot")

ggseasonplot(ts)

ggsubseriesplot(ts)

ggAcf(ts)

ggPacf(ts)

decomposed_ts <- decompose(ts)
plot(decomposed_ts)
